            The system includes an <a href="/alfa-laval-nx-418-decanter-centrifuge/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317] underline">Alfa Laval decanter centrifuge</a>, an electric preheater, a clean oil tank with pumps, and a fully automatic control system. The optional sludge auger is provided to move the sludge from underneath the decanter sludge chute away from the decanter base.
