        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">Sunflower Oil (Oil Seed)</h3>
        <figure class="mb-6">
          <img
            src="/images/decanter-centrifuge-applications/Alfa-Laval-NX-314-Decanter-Centrifuge-for-Sunflower-Oil.jpg"
            alt="Alfa Laval NX-314 Decanter Centrifuge for Sunflower Oil"
