            <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center font-['Source_Sans_3']">Alfa Laval THC Cannabis Biomass Separation - Solvent</figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure>
            <img
              src="/images/decanter-centrifuge-applications/Alfa-Laval-NX418-Decanter-C1D2-for-Hemp-Ethanol-Processing-Texted-1000-1.jpg"
